{"id": 1794, "genre": 1000, "title": "你都看破了哪些店铺命名的套路？", "description": "店铺升级第一步——起个体面（装腔作势）的店名 。（题图来自：林小妖）", "record_count": 15488, "comment_count": 58, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170710182340GPTkjBXyL0Ao8fhW.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-07-11T17:00:46Z", "questions": [{"id": 2586, "title": "你都看破了哪些店铺命名的套路？", "content": "你都看破了哪些店铺命名的套路？ ", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 220361, "content": "干不过连锁健身房的小型健身房，就叫健身工作室", "image": "img/option/option/20170710174119ReFEKUqAVXcWv7zL.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 220362, "content": "餐厅不能叫小吃美食，后缀要改成 “轻食”“小馆”“食肆” ", "image": "img/option/option/20170710174324mtdOjRgVqHAExB6n.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 220363, "content": "有出息的书店要叫“书局”“空间”…总之不能平铺直叙叫书店", "image": "img/option/option/20170710175630O01vuaIXShLKVlFx.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 220366, "content": "品牌年轻化绝招，推出品牌名后面加个“YOUNG”的副品牌", "image": "img/option/option/20170710175502Vr8S4PnKk19myqRB.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 220367, "content": "衣服食物放一间里卖的都叫“生活方式体验店”", "image": "img/option/option/20170710180346B8X9QTfk30sGmv7d.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 220369, "content": " 名创优品、良品铺子……本土杂货店不是“良品”就“优品”", "image": "img/option/option/20170710180357jvILgk9zPylJ6hNR.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 220370, "content": "淘宝卖日式杂货文具的基本都叫xx生活馆", "image": "img/option/option/20170710180739SgH2Awsk5avnMylJ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 220371, "content": "首饰杂物类的三无产品，现如今都叫手作", "image": "img/option/option/20170710181912QpEOr07DqVbSmcNA.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}